<![CDATA[<div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">Dear&nbsp;{!Outbound_Notification__c.Contact_First_Name__c}&nbsp;{!Outbound_Notification__c.Contact_Last_Name__c}</font></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1"><br></font></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">I hereby confirm that we have received your R800 registration fee. Please note this fee is non-refundable.&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1"><br></font></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">To secure your registration for&nbsp;{!Outbound_Notification__c.Current_Date_Year__c}, please submit the following documentation and make the following payment&nbsp;and as soon as possible so that we can process your student number:</font></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1"><br></font></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;">	</span>Completed and signed registration forms</font></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;">	</span>Signed Repayment Calculator</font></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;">	</span>Signed Addendum A</font></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;">	</span>Signed Social Indemnity form&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;">	</span>A copy of student’s ID</font></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;">	</span>A copy of sponsor’s ID</font></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1"><br></font></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">Please contact me in order to confirm that I have received all documentation after it has been sent. Faxed and e-mailed documentation will be accepted; however the originals must be submitted upon enrolment on&nbsp;{!Outbound_Notification__c.Academic_Start_Date__c}.</font></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1"><br></font></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">In order to secure the&nbsp;{!Outbound_Notification__c.Earlybird__c} fees, an early-bird deposit is required on or&nbsp;before&nbsp;{!Outbound_Notification__c.Early_Bird_Date__c}. The early-bird&nbsp;deposit, excluding the registration fee, will be deducted from the first month’s&nbsp;payment. Please note however, failure to pay the early-bird deposit will result in the&nbsp;{!Outbound_Notification__c.Academic_Start_Date_Year__c}&nbsp;fees being applicable (estimated&nbsp;increase of 8%-15% in&nbsp;{!Outbound_Notification__c.Current_Date_Year__c}).</font></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1"><br></font></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">If you require any further information please do not hesitate to contact me.</font></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1"><br></font></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">Kind Regards</font></div><div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">{!Outbound_Notification__c.Sender_Name__c}</font></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">{!Outbound_Notification__c.Campus__c}</font></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">{!Outbound_Notification__c.Sender_Email__c}</font></div></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1"><br></font></div><div><span style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 6pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">CTI and MGI are part of Pearson, the world’s leading learning company. Pearson is the corporate owner, not a registered provider nor conferrer of qualifications. CTI and MGI are registered PHEI and offer separate qualifications in South Africa. CTI Education Group (PTY) Ltd. is registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training as a private higher education institution under the Higher Education Act, 101, of 1997. Registration Certificate number: 2004/HE07/004. www.cti.ac.za. Midrand Graduate Institute (PTY) Ltd. T/A MGI is registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training as a private higher education institution under the Higher Education Act, 101, of 1997. Registration Certificate number: 2001/HE07/008.&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.mgi.ac.za/" style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: x-small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 6pt;">www.mgi.ac.za</span></a><span style="font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 6pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">.</span></div><div><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1"><br></font></div>]]></td>
